2007-07-19  Sebastien Merle  <sebastien@fluendo.com>

	* flumotion/transcoder/log.py (Loggable.warnAndRaise,
	  LoggerProxy.logFailure, LoggerProxy.logException,
	  LoggerProxy.warnAndRaise):
